There's not to much to talk about for a movie of this sort.  The movie did meet my expectations, but at the same time it diminished my taste for the rest of the film.  Our hero is a dull, shy guy who couldn't get a girl to save his life, but after joining a drama club in his school he couldn't shake them.  I'm not sure what's going on with the camera angles or if this is what the director was after, but apparently white and some with strawberries panties were in every shot and they were shown a lot.  The only thing that I could think of at the time was 'if I could get into half the trouble as he could I could die happy.'

I enjoyed watching this film because there are a couple or more girls with large breasts.  The story behind all the sex scenes is good. Therefore, I recommend it to all adults who enjoy watching anime.

I bought this series cause it was deleted through a sight I go to for new or old H-series. Anyway this series is really nice and the animation is done very well. Nice scenes all around. But here's a little summary...

Shindo Nikita has a secret that he has been hiding for a long time--he loves hentai and H-games. He enters "The Alternative Trivia Research Club", where the first of his many sexual encounters takes place. Despite that, he finds out that both of his foster sisters are in love with him, and he has to make a choice--who he really loves.

Now for those who don't know there is a 3rd vol. to this so also check that out especially if you loved the first two volumes.
